{"tid":2339543,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"［分析］要珍惜聖誕節，過多幾年香港可能再冇聖誕。","createTime":"2020-12-24T17:02:12.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-21T16:55:01.000Z","uid":219007,"like":18,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"75a48bdd7920958740d694946da9d051b0485ba5","tid":2339543,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T17:02:12.000Z","msg":"論華人比較大影響力嘅地方，中國大陸同台灣係冇聖誕假放，背景原因大陸唔使講，台灣就因為佢從來都唔係一個親西方文化嘅地方。 反而香港前身英國殖民地所以有假放。 而台灣因為商業因素近十幾年先開始有聖誕氣氛。<br />\n<br />\n但係隨着香港係中國眼中係未收復人心下，大一統換血就必然。而其中一個辦法就係減退香港嘅西方文化，清洗聖誕文化好有可能係目標之一。 只要從商業利誘入手，同商家講好數唔好注事聖誕節（冇撒資嘅企業自然會聽佢講），再俾少少其他着數佢，客觀要減退聖誕文化應該唔難，<br />\n慢慢三五七之後再取消聖誕假期絕對唔出奇，五年前你都冇諗過會立國安法。到是香港人亦都唔會有感覺，因為香港早已經淪為極權統治地方。<br />\n<br />\n所以呢幾年我認為要珍惜聖誕節，活在當下。將來有機會再去外國過，聖誕氣氛肯定仲濃厚。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de77fa5d42410d52ba22d81798f72f3b073b45c3","tid":2339543,"uid":54927,"like":2,"dislike":10,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T17:59:59.000Z","msg":"聖你老母咩香港人有幾多個信耶穌<br />\n大家都係要一日假期出嚟爆房飲飲食食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n都係比嗰啲商家老屈錢嘅日子"},{"pid":"4e3488942449640aaec83fc30528d9856ec4348f","tid":2339543,"uid":164497,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"de77fa5d42410d52ba22d81798f72f3b073b45c3","tid":2339543,"uid":54927,"like":2,"dislike":10,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T17:59:59.000Z","msg":"聖你老母咩香港人有幾多個信耶穌<br />\n大家都係要一日假期出嚟爆房飲飲食食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n都係比嗰啲商家老屈錢嘅日子"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T18:55:41.000Z","msg":"好多人信耶穌<br />\n但同屈原節同一個道理<br />\n邊個會特登食粽果陣諗佢"},{"pid":"7fd15dcb3b463765ee5f2d2d943d70959cc4adc3","tid":2339543,"uid":67208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T00:04:08.000Z","msg":"仲有澳門"},{"pid":"f7bc8f1f009bd7515c37b17dc80ee67c41be6254","tid":2339543,"uid":194120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T00:24:19.000Z","msg":"假照放不過改名毛主席誕辰"},{"pid":"3413f1ec3fe903a6a25660376fb2c1b1892dcf6c","tid":2339543,"uid":237459,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T00:26:09.000Z","msg":"香港今年已經無聖誕啦<br />\n你有得出去食晚飯咩柒頭"},{"pid":"6f2996046eb2f9d7b9cd737135c8d7507fb88465","tid":2339543,"uid":11067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T00:26:19.000Z","msg":"施永青：最撚憎聖誕節"},{"pid":"1a22903ad721ba0a5255892b686a0f67b57773cd","tid":2339543,"uid":192465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T00:57:06.000Z","msg":"耶稣是中国人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc6a2644b060adfcd8a72ad070c653c55035a528","tid":2339543,"uid":46736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T01:38:24.000Z","msg":"仲有復活節<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7c97a80d0fd35203e4040c4fa64def2824d9675","tid":2339543,"uid":292544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T02:02:47.000Z","msg":"以後跟大陸人放假<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/shocking_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/shocking_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/shocking_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1472c7f58062c0cb454d4cc211f69dcdeae806ba","tid":2339543,"uid":161711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T16:55:01.000Z","msg":"淨係會寫seasons greetings<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}